elliottt opened PR #4809 from trevor/move-nop-to-isle to main:

Lower nop in ISLE in the x64 backend, and remove the final Ok(()) from the lower function to assert that all cases that fall through will panic.

elliottt edited PR #4809 from trevor/move-nop-to-isle to main:

Lower nop in ISLE in the x64 backend, and remove the final Ok(()) from the lower function to assert that all cases that aren't handled in ISLE will panic.
